    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that makes sense. some of the committee members are saying that these regs aren't even really about the environment anymore, but are just a way to kneecap domestic manufacturing in favor of foreign companies that don't have to deal with this stuff. do you think there's any truth to the idea that these policies are more about political ideology than actual environmental science?",
